588
00:31:45,710 --> 00:31:47,890
Design speaks of meaning,

589
00:31:48,280 --> 00:31:50,290
while belief speaks of hope.

590
00:31:50,960 --> 00:31:52,490
And all prophecies

591
00:31:52,660 --> 00:31:55,210
allow us to hear our hearts more deeply.

592
00:31:56,970 --> 00:32:00,510
Don't let superstition
control our thoughts.

593
00:32:01,800 --> 00:32:03,400
But let reason and heart

594
00:32:03,640 --> 00:32:05,590
work together.

595
00:32:06,290 --> 00:32:10,200
Then we'll be able to determine
our own life path.

596
00:32:10,540 --> 00:32:11,450
Thank you so much.

597
00:32:21,100 --> 00:32:22,070
I'd like to thank

598
00:32:22,090 --> 00:32:24,930
Ritt Sitthisakunphong again

599
00:32:24,970 --> 00:32:27,730
for speaking about belief.

600
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:30,600
And I believe that everyone knows that

601
00:32:30,690 --> 00:32:33,850
