602
00:32:33,890 --> 00:32:35,800
Belief shouldn't become a superstition,

603
00:32:35,840 --> 00:32:38,190
but an inspiration

604
00:32:38,230 --> 00:32:41,560
for us to keep going on.

605
00:32:41,650 --> 00:32:44,300
This is a special moment

606
00:32:44,340 --> 00:32:46,780
